[COLOR dodgerblue][B]Version 2.2.05[/B][/COLOR]
- Added TMDB Lists integration
	- Import from Trakt lists (large lists are split into 100 item chunks)
	- Create / Delete / Clear lists from My Lists > TMDB My Lists
